{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_177","type":"agent_message","text":"Implemented the past-sessions-first home screen end to end. The backend now exposes real list/create session endpoints in [sessions.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/api/v1/routes/sessions.py), and the frontend home route was rebuilt around live session data in [HomePage.tsx](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/frontend/src/pages/home/HomePage.tsx) with grouped active/completed cards, loading/empty/error states, and a working `Start a new session` action. I also added a small frontend sessions client in [sessions.ts](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/frontend/src/api/sessions.ts) and updated tests for the new route behavior.\n\nVerification passed at the code level:\n- `python -m pytest backend/tests -q` -> `51 passed, 5 skipped`\n- `python -m ruff check backend/app backend/tests/test_session_api.py backend/tests/test_health.py backend/tests/test_session_service.py`\n- `python -m compileall backend/app backend/tests/test_session_api.py`\n- `npm --prefix frontend run test` -> `10 passed`\n- `npm --prefix frontend run lint`\n- `npm --prefix frontend run build`\n\nBrowser artifacts were captured at:\n- `.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-21-home-desktop.png`\n- `.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-21-home-mobile.png`\n- `.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-21-new-session-workspace.png`\n\nThe required reviewer summary file was written to [21-past-sessions-home-screen.summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/prompts/21-past-sessions-home-screen.summary.md). It also documents the one notable local-env issue: the compose backend could not start because the existing local `secrets.yaml` contains keys the current settings schema rejects, so browser QA used a temporary SQLite-backed QA backend/frontend instead of modifying local secrets or persistent Postgres data."}}
{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_37","type":"todo_list","items":[{"text":"Add backend DB dependency and versioned session list/create endpoints with tests","completed":false},{"text":"Build frontend sessions home screen with real data loading, filtering/grouping, and new-session action plus tests","completed":false},{"text":"Run verification, capture browser screenshots, commit checkpoints, and write the final summary file","completed":false}]}}
